row.field:
XML 파싱할 때, expat 안쓰고 MSXML을 쓰는 예제입니다.
Win32::OLE 모듈을 사용하고요, 파이썬의 win32com.client 를 쓸때보다 좀 쉬워요. in, with를 써서 OLE 콜렉션을 foreach로 이터레이션할 수 있거든요.

<code>
use Win32::OLE qw(in with); 

my $DOM_document = Win32::OLE->new('Microsoft.XMLDom') or die "couldn't creat!"; 

$DOM_document->{async} = "False"; 
$DOM_document->{validateOnParse} = "True"; 

my $xml_str=<<ENDOFXML; 
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="euc-kr" ?> 
<root> 
    <name>Lee Ho Jin</name> 
    <phone>11111111</phone> 
    <address>Seoul</address> 
</root> 
ENDOFXML 

$DOM_document->LoadXML($xml_str) or die "didn't load!"; 
my $root = $DOM_document->DocumentElement; 

my $childNodes = $root->childNodes; 

foreach $childNode (in $childNodes) 
{ 
    print $childNode->nodeName.":"; 
} 
</code>

