client:
<code>
use LWP::UserAgent;

my @urls = (
'http://localhost/env.cgi',
'http://localhost/env1.cgi',
);

my $ua = new LWP::UserAgent;
$ua->timeout(8);

foreach my $url (@urls) {
    print "processing $url... \n";
    my $start = time;
    my $request = new HTTP::Request GET => $url;
    my $response = $ua->request($request);
    my $used = time() - $start;
    if ($response->is_success) {
        print "succeeded: $used sec.\n";
    } else {
        print "failed: $used sec.\n";
    }
}
</code>
저는 위 test에서 두개의 요청 모두 timeout 처리가 정상적으로 됩니다.


